The paper discusses security threats and proposes a security model for the Internet of Things and Services. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Computer Security (cs.CR) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). The proposed model involves autonomous systems, which could fall under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the architecture of the proposed model, which could fall under the categories of Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC).
